"SmartSource:Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md": {"path":"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md","class_name":"SmartSource","history":[{"blocks":{"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**1. \"Blink: The Power of Thinking Without Thinking\" by Malcolm Gladwell**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**2. \"Predictably Irrational: The Hidden Forces That Shape Our Decisions\" by Dan Ariely**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**3. \"Nudge: Improving Decisions About Health, Wealth, and Happiness\" by Richard H. Thaler and Cass R. Sunstein**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**4. \"The Undoing Project: A Friendship That Changed Our Minds\" by Michael Lewis**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**5. \"Misbehaving: The Making of Behavioral Economics\" by Richard H. Thaler**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**6. \"Influence: The Psychology of Persuasion\" by Robert B. Cialdini**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**7. \"Thinking in Bets: Making Smarter Decisions When You Don't Have All the Facts\" by Annie Duke**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**8. \"The Power of Habit: Why We Do What We Do in Life and Business\" by Charles Duhigg**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**9. \"Superforecasting: The Art and Science of Prediction\" by Philip E. Tetlock and Dan Gardner**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**10. \"Sway: The Irresistible Pull of Irrational Behavior\" by Ori Brafman and Rom Brafman**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**11. \"Fooled by Randomness: The Hidden Role of Chance in Life and in the Markets\" by Nassim Nicholas Taleb**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**12. \"Quiet: The Power of Introverts in a World That Can't Stop Talking\" by Susan Cain**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**13. \"Drive: The Surprising Truth About What Motivates Us\" by Daniel H. Pink**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**14. \"Thinking in Systems: A Primer\" by Donella H. Meadows**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**15. \"Scarcity: Why Having Too Little Means So Much\" by Sendhil Mullainathan and Eldar Shafir**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#{1}":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**1. \"Deep Work: Rules for Focused Success in a Distracted World\" by Cal Newport**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**2. \"Make It Stick: The Science of Successful Learning\" by Peter C. Brown, Henry L. Roediger III, and Mark A. McDaniel**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**3. \"Atomic Habits: An Easy & Proven Way to Build Good Habits & Break Bad Ones\" by James Clear**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**4. \"The Organized Mind: Thinking Straight in the Age of Information Overload\" by Daniel J. Levitin**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**5. \"A Mind for Numbers: How to Excel at Math and Science (Even If You Flunked Algebra)\" by Barbara Oakley**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**6. \"The Productivity Project: Accomplishing More by Managing Your Time, Attention, and Energy\" by Chris Bailey**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**7. \"Ultralearning: Master Hard Skills, Outsmart the Competition, and Accelerate Your Career\" by Scott H. Young**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**8. \"The Art of Learning: An Inner Journey to Optimal Performance\" by Josh Waitzkin**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**9. \"Essentialism: The Disciplined Pursuit of Less\" by Greg McKeown**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**10. \"Flow: The Psychology of Optimal Experience\" by Mihaly Csikszentmihalyi**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**11. \"The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People: Powerful Lessons in Personal Change\" by Stephen R. Covey**":true,"Sources/Book Notes/Books - Thinking.md#**12. \"Mindset: The New Psychology of Success\" by Carol S. Dweck**":true,"Sources/Book N